{
  "texts": [
    "In the next section, we assess the alignment methods, highlighting their strengths and weaknesses.",
    "Description.",
    "In this section, we assess the alignment methods across three scenarios: 1) fine-tuning an SFT model with alignment methods, 2) finetuning a pre-trained model with alignment methods, and 3) fine-tuning an instruction-tuned model with alignment methods.",
    "Subsequently, within each scenario, we examine their performance across reasoning, mathematical problem-solving, truthfulness, question-answering, and multi-task understanding.",
    "Details regarding these scenarios are provided in the following section."
  ]
}